    make
    make test
    make tardist

CREATE NEW VERSION (FOR DEVELOPER ONLY)

    * README           -- In documentation
    * CHANGES          -- Result of command: localtime | gclip
    * lib/WWW/MLite.pm -- In documentation (VERSION) & in code $VERSION
